WEBVTT

00:00:02.273 --> 00:00:05.943 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It can be hard to put faith
in something you cannot see.

00:00:07.736 --> 00:00:10.072 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But real faith is not blind.

00:00:12.199 --> 00:00:14.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Real faith is based on facts,

00:00:15.327 --> 00:00:17.329 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on realities,

00:00:19.290 --> 00:00:21.292 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on truth.

00:00:23.502 --> 00:00:25.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It gives us courage and strength,

00:00:28.257 --> 00:00:30.301 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it helps us to endure.

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:36.348 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When life gets hard, it provides peace.

00:00:36.348 --> 00:00:40.019 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It reminds us of our purpose,

00:00:40.019 --> 00:00:42.605 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it brings us real joy.

00:00:45.566 --> 00:00:47.860 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Learn how to build and strengthen your faith

00:00:47.860 --> 00:00:52.156 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at the 2021 “Powerful by Faith!”
Convention of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

